[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "これで……終わりだよ！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ひ、ひぃっ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ハイディ、あちらにお父様が逃げていきます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ったく、逃げ足だけは昔から速いんだから……。\n家出してから鍛えた追跡術、見せてやるか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "父さん、もう逃げられないよ。\n観念して話して",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "許してくれ！\n本気で決闘がしたいわけじゃなかったんだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ただ母さんに、俺の知識を認めてもらいたくて……\n考古学の知見で勝負しようと……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "はあ？　なら、なんでゴーレムを使って暴れたのさ。\n知識で勝負するつもりだったんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "仕方ないだろう？　まずこれくらいやらないと\n見向きもされないまま捨てられてしまう……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "捨てられるって……じゃあ、そもそも不正なんか\nしなければよかったじゃん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……母さんは優秀だ。\n父さんなんか足元にも及ばない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "でも、俺は母さんに認められたいんだ。\n対等な関係になりたかった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうじゃないと捨てられてしまう。\nだから……功績が欲しくて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……馬鹿じゃないの。それ、母さんに言ったわけ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "こんな気持ち、言えるものか！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "つべこべ言ってる場合じゃないでしょ！\nまったくもう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "私から母さんに、父さんと話すようには言ってみるよ。\nでも、今話したこと、ちゃんと母さんにも言いな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……私に認められたかった？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "すまん、この通りだ！　\nどうか俺とやり直してくれ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あのね、自分勝手に家を出て、挙句に決闘だなんて\n言う人のこと、そう簡単に許せると思う？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "め、面目次第もございません……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……こりゃあ、時間掛かりそうだなぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "もう、逃げないんですよね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……気が済むまで見守ってやるか。\n家出してた分、それくらいの親孝行はしないとね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]